{"tid":1658813,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"關於陳彥霖cctv係演員扮ge陰謀，我覺得大家可以留意下呢個位","createTime":"2019-10-16T15:34:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-14T16:47:39.000Z","uid":236914,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"555f40effdc499ab2fb9238aa59e5e13fadd648f","tid":1658813,"uid":236914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T15:34:15.000Z","msg":"小妹有一個愚昧ge睇法，歡迎大家討論<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9EzfwoY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9EzfwoY.png&h=263b281d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n趙羅尼話唔同ge鏡頭、角度會顯到個人有唔同<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yFSEdBT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyFSEdBT.jpg&h=1911f94d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁假設我地唔肯定cctv中ge陳彥霖係咪演員扮，我就當話cctv可能影到個人ge輪廓同自拍有出入<br />\n咁髮轉呢？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qMARPbi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqMARPbi.jpg&h=574e1cbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n髮轉係天生無得改變，左邊兩幅，髮轉下面係有baby hair向左轉，而陳妹妹係無baby hair兼且中間分界利落<br />\n就算係分左界，就算佢真係有baby hair，佢ge baby hair都唔會突然消失<br />\n我就有baby hair，無論我分邊個界都好，d baby hair都係會係到<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vwHkHzb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvwHkHzb.jpg&h=bf204f5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我再睇返佢自拍ge片段，nope , still no baby hair"},{"pid":"edc390416fed2c7e1a06476e2e951adf82a1cb99","tid":1658813,"uid":236914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T15:35:33.000Z","msg":"推1"},{"pid":"4167540d846ab9e20e6bee9893a1ba6f6779b204","tid":1658813,"uid":236914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T15:35:44.000Z","msg":"推2"},{"pid":"809321ffe11fcc50493ef1a867510cedc35485a4","tid":1658813,"uid":236914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T15:36:27.000Z","msg":"推3"},{"pid":"4f0b1ed1cad2f34d71bb709ce62227718b4951ca","tid":1658813,"uid":236914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"